organic.title: Women's Center-High Desert
organic.snippet: We offer non-judgmental services to all members of the community who are survivors of domestic violence, sexual assault, family violence, and human trafficking.

organic.title: Services 4 - Women's Center-High Desert
organic.snippet: We are able to offer safe shelter, food, and clothing. The staff and volunteers for the shelter offer a 24-hour hotline for victims of domestic violence.
